The '''buff-breasted babbler''' ('''''Pellorneum tickelli''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Pellorneidae]]. It is found in [[Bangladesh]], [[Cambodia]], [[China]], [[India]], [[Laos]], [[Malaysia]], [[Myanmar]], [[Thailand]], and [[Vietnam]]. Its natural [[habitat]]s are [[subtropical or tropical moist lowland forest]] and subtropical or tropical moist [[montane forest]].

